<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DropIn | A IA que te entende</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0d0e12;
            --card-bg: #161822;
            --accent-color: #ff3366;
            --text-color: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #8a8f98;
            --chat-user: #3a3f58;
            --chat-ia: #252836;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        body { background-color: var(--bg-color); color: var(--text-color); overflow-x: hidden; }
        header { display: flex; padding: 2rem 5%; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .logo span { color: var(--accent-color); }
        .hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; padding: 2rem 5%; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; align-items: center; }
        @media (min-width: 768px) { .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; min-height: 80vh; } }
        .hero-text h1 { font-size: 3rem; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; }
        .hero-text h1 span { color: var(--accent-color); }
        .hero-text p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
        .chat-mockup { background-color: var(--card-bg); border-radius: 24px; padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #252836; box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 480px; }
        .chat-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #252836; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .avatar { width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: var(--accent-color); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        .status-info h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; }
        .status-info p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #00ff66; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
        .status-info p::before { content: ''; display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 6px; background-color: #00ff66; border-radius: 50%; }
        .chat-messages { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.8rem; overflow-y: auto; padding-right: 5px; }
        .msg { max-width: 85%; padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 18px; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-word; }
        .msg.ia { background-color: var(--chat-ia); align-self: flex-start; border-top-left-radius: 4px; }
        .msg.user { background-color: var(--chat-user); align-self: flex-end; border-top-right-radius: 4px; }
        .msg.loading { color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; background: transparent; }
        .chat-input-area { margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; gap: 10px; background: #0d0e12; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 50px; border: 1px solid #252836; }
        .chat-input-area input { flex: 1; background: transparent; border: none; color: white; padding-left: 1rem; outline: none; }
        .send-btn { background: var(--accent-color); border: none; width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%; color: white; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header><div class="logo">DROP<span>IN</span></div></header>
    <main class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Sem textão.<br>Só o <span>papo reto</span>.</h1>
            <p>A primeira inteligência artificial que fala a sua língua. Gírias, memes e a vibe que você já conhece.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-mockup">
            <div class="chat-header">
                <div class="avatar">⚡</div>
                <div class="status-info"><h3>DropIn (IA)</h3><p>online e de boa</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="chat-messages" id="chatMessages">
                <div class="msg ia">Salve! E aí, de boa? Manda a braba.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="chat-input-area">
                <input type="text" id="userInput" placeholder="Escreve algo aí..." autocomplete="off">
                <button class="send-btn" id="sendBtn">➔</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
